                "title": "Plama Lawa"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/181140897/b81f8bd6ae1e5b5f53807a4cd0704469_7351025800500327212.png",
                "id": "talent61494",
                "key": "Movo Lawa",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Movo Lawa"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成5點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/181140897/36768cf2c0fc7aafe7c6c956fee29fba_1716470824499592484.png",
                "id": "talent82272",
                "key": "Upa Shato",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Upa Shato"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被動技能</span></p><p>【被動】戰鬥開始時，初始附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">岩盔</span>和<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">堅岩之力</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">岩盔</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附屬角色受到傷害時：</span>抵消1點傷害。抵消<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩傷害</span>時，需額外消耗一次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：3</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">堅岩之力</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p>角色造成的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>變爲<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">每回合一次：</span>角色造成的傷害+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">角色所附屬的「岩盔」被移除後：</span>也移除此狀態。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/10/84496276/370c275e0af4838e7689aa8e24bc36c7_462299518970138293.png",
                "id": "talent14872",
                "key": "魔化：岩盔",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "魔化：岩盔"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附著的元素發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（冰）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（水）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（火）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（雷）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_4217783846919239083.png",
                "id": "talent18899",
                "key": "岩元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "岩元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗一層可用次數；</p><p>可用次數耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_3698628524351828554.png",
